{"tid":1645552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無可否認一個事實，連登已經開始失效","createTime":"2019-10-11T02:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:13:12.000Z","uid":56260,"like":147,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"7cdc229fdb307d529a4ffcfc8f5a29461b159ea8","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:33:16.000Z","msg":"四個月喇，同路人一路都只係諗緊點樣維持團火<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但對家已經有晒充足時間同資源鋪路</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論滲透連登、TG甚至更多私人媒體 (e.g. 被_人士)<br />\n<br />\n所以連登既熱門係咩、吹緊咩風<br />\n其實已經唔再重要<br />\n因為你要為左睇呢啲post、睇今日捉吹咩風<br />\n花呢一丁點精力都已經係對家既一種策略<br />\n已經俾人安插晒資源喺度<span style=\"color: red;\">打緊泥漿戰</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳小姐事件都一樣<br />\n十個人聽完有十種諗法，疑幻疑真<br />\n但除左做實事(鼓勵更多真相出現、保護佢人身等)之外<br />\n鼓吹任何其他言論，對運動整體都係無補於事<br />\n<br />\n所以敬告各連登仔女<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是最貼地、最亢奮、最同仇敵愾既各位同學</span><br />\n我地要記住<span style=\"color: orange;\">運動初心</span>，悲憤之中時刻<span style=\"color: orange;\">保持清醒</span><br />\n叫自己一定要堅持堅持，千祈唔好俾連登帶咩風向影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好想每一位年紀比我細既同路人<br />\n可以透過自己既智慧，安然無恙照顧好自己<br />\n他日煲底相見，我希望可以俾你地<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">一個最真切、最溫柔既擁抱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680dc6728d44dd517b659fe67a083a773061c31b","tid":1645552,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b354bff7b66de0ca0539b8c7d3d0faacf288789a","tid":1645552,"uid":264128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:35:00.000Z","msg":"對抗警暴，1011 十八區開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644865</a>"},{"pid":"d40f79e8b20eb6ae44924142222aa0057c728afb","tid":1645552,"uid":172141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:35:05.000Z","msg":"煲底見"},{"pid":"b17b7e8bcb81259cb9b24d6502ba583bc3f57074","tid":1645552,"uid":121086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:35:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3bbad8c3391fe561bc946e89da42f254b6af628","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"認清現實係越黎越難<br />\n但我地一定可以煲底相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6061bb2ed762d2b6fad503e0a1a03a7b5de856b","tid":1645552,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求連登關閉一個月</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5795e30b903902c2bde73b97cceded8d545066f","tid":1645552,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:36:49.000Z","msg":"少左好多行動ost"},{"pid":"d7f66cbef9ada9393526c26a8849cdbc3941361e","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a5795e30b903902c2bde73b97cceded8d545066f","tid":1645552,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:36:49.000Z","msg":"少左好多行動ost"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"正正係呢篇文既重點<br />\n少左係好合理，因為對家有晒各種手段壓制<br />\n四個月，連登變晒架喇<br />\n今時今日唔好過分強求連登成版行動post啦"},{"pid":"cf1a1e2e1552372ebdc6085f742e4a6a30769444","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80f5f0bb6ad51217122b7b90993736667944fee3","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0215d8f59e02eba0b62fad820749df58d7bdb737","tid":1645552,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"88900c0021b4922eea47334451fbc8a50243aace","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":3,"