得十幾人支持，好傷心<br />\n係，我無Fact check，但係我情願相信，呢個世界有人願意冒被捕風險，都要做眾籌<br />\n希望大家衡量過後，可以支持做實事嘅團隊。<br />\n件事未完，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸贏都好，保護手足應該係和理非最需要關心嘅事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1643523/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fpayments%2F%3Foid%3D1662043%26err%3D1&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=cde50e48\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/payments/?oid=1662043&amp;err=1</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJhHcCt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJhHcCt.jpg&h=5bcbfa54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a984c4459f8e20729e45d1387f179574de9dec58","tid":1645552,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6da83d4fa8c48742dd4cb576cb7d0ea1805c87e5","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467197b0ff7dd37c95bf467df4aa87650fade5db","tid":1645552,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f66cbef9ada9393526c26a8849cdbc3941361e","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"正正係呢篇文既重點<br />\n少左係好合理，因為對家有晒各種手段壓制<br />\n四個月，連登變晒架喇<br />\n今時今日唔好過分強求連登成版行動post啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"因為真係諗唔到新嘢<br />\n暫時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"網上可以玩下國際戰線、文宣<br />\n現實暫時的確唔容易聚到人行動<br />\n但時機要黎就自然會黎<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">潛龍勿用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f54a681c478e831dc01377da611dc23eac4081","tid":1645552,"uid":56260,"like